item.title: Text Actor Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: yoyokits
item.content:encoded:
• Text Actor is developed by Yohanes Wahyu Nurcahyo
  • The user data are not collected at all
  • The text written in the application will be saved locally on the device
  • Because there is no user data are collected then there is no processed user data
  • There is no third parties who can use the user data using any widgets like social buttons or social media connect
  • We don’t notify user if the software are updated, except if Google do so
  • This privacy policy is valid from March 15th, 2024 to March 15th, 2025
